trans-unit.source: Exposes <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableCell"></xref> types to UI Automation.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TableCellAutomationPeer"></xref> class.
The <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableCell"></xref> that is associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TableCellAutomationPeer"></xref>.
Gets the control type for the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableCell"></xref> that is associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TableCellAutomationPeer"></xref>.
This method is called by <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlType"></xref>.
The <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationControlType.Custom"></xref> enumeration value.
Gets the name of the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableCell"></xref> that is associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TableCellAutomationPeer"></xref>.
This method is called by <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetClassName"></xref>.
A string that contains "TableCell".

Gets the localized version of the control type for the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableCell"></xref> that is associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TableCellAutomationPeer"></xref>.
A string that contains "cell".
Gets the control pattern for the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableCell"></xref> that is associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TableCellAutomationPeer"></xref>.
A value from the enumeration.
If patternInterface is , this method returns the current instance of the ; otherwise, this method returns `null`.

Gets or sets a value that indicates whether the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableCell"></xref> that is associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TableCellAutomationPeer"></xref> is understood by the end user as interactive or as contributing to the logical structure of the control in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_gui](~/includes/tla2sharptla-gui-md.md)].
This method is called by <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.IsControlElement"></xref>.
`true`.
Gets the ordinal number of the column that contains the cell or item.
This member is an explicit interface member implementation.
It can be used only when the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TableCellAutomationPeer> instance is cast to an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IGridItemProvider> interface.
A zero-based ordinal number that identifies the column containing the cell or item.
Gets the number of columns spanned by a cell or item.
This member is an explicit interface member implementation.
It can be used only when the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TableCellAutomationPeer> instance is cast to an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IGridItemProvider> interface.
The number of columns spanned.
Gets a UI Automation provider that implements <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern"></xref> and represents the container of the cell or item.
This member is an explicit interface member implementation.
It can be used only when the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TableCellAutomationPeer> instance is cast to an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IGridItemProvider> interface.
A UI Automation provider that implements the <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern"></xref> and represents the cell or item container.

It can be used only when the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TableCellAutomationPeer> instance is cast to an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.IGridItemProvider> interface.
The number of rows spanned.
